Level 1<br>
Mana: 10 x (Target's Level) mana<br>
Casting Time: (Target's Level) / 8 seconds<br>
Duration: 3 x (Target's Level) seconds<br>
Recast Time: 3 x (Last Target's Level) seconds<br>
<br>
This spell can be cast on any Player Character that is of the same or lower level as the Wizard.  It causes an extra fire-based attack (proc) every time that character's weapon strikes a target.  The damage done by the extra attack is 33% of the normal damage that weapon is capable of inflicting.  (If his weapon normally does between 30 and 60 points of damage each hit, this spell will cause additional damage of between 10 and 20 points of fire damage for each hit.)<br>
<br>
Also:<br>
<br>
Infusion of E'ci<br>
Level 4<br>
 -- Same as above except damage is cold-based<br>
<br>
Infusion of Thunder<br>
Level 8<br>
 -- Same as above except damage is magic-based<br>
<br>
-----------------------<br>
<br>
Saturation of Ro<br>
Level 32<br>
 -- Same as above except damage is fire-based and 66% of attack damage.<br>
<br>
Saturation of E'ci<br>
Level 36<br>
 -- Same as above except damage is cold-based and 66% of attack damage.<br>
<br>
Saturation of Thunder<br>
Level 40<br>
 -- Same as above except damage is magic-based and 66% of attack damage.<br>
<br>
<br>
-----------------------<br>
<br>
Embodiment of Ro<br>
Level 52<br>
 -- Same as above except damage is fire-based and 80% of attack damage.<br>
<br>
Embodiment of E'ci<br>
Level 56<br>
 -- Same as above except damage is cold-based and 80% of attack damage.<br>
<br>
Embodiment of Thunder<br>
Level 60<br>
 -- Same as above except damage is magic-based and 80% of attack damage.<br>
<br>
<br>
Comments?<br>
<br>
-Raystonn<br>
